{
  "texts": [
    "• FinBen (Xie et al, 2024).",
    "The FinBen dataset provides a thorough and comprehensive assessment of LLMs' financial capabilities.",
    "It integrates 35 existing datasets covering 23 financial tasks.",
    "The creators have categorized the tasks into three difficulty levels: foundamental tasks, advanced cognitive engagement, and general intelligence.",
    "FinBen extends financial evaluation to a wide range of tasks including quantification, understanding, forecasting, and introduces the direct trading task for the first time."
  ]
}